!TP_LOCALLAB_BWCIE_TOOLTIP;Only usable in Global mode or if Scope is set to 100.\nThe 'Black and White' option shows only the luminance in the histogram making it easier to adjust the shadows and highlights when using the Gamma and Slope sliders and the Tone Mapping Operators.
