!TP_SHARPENING_CAP;Capture Deconvolution
!TP_SHARPENING_CAPFRAME;Corner boost
!TP_SHARPENING_CONTRASTAUTO_TOOLTIP;Auto contrast level estimation.\nValue subject to variation depending on position in preview.\nBe careful, disable auto after estimation.
