!TP_SHARPENING_RADIUS_PROTSE_TOOLTIP;Defines the central protection area % (Full image or geographical RT-spot center) that will not be affected by 'Corner radius boost'.\nThe results in the TIF/JPG outputs correspond to those of 'fit to screen'.
